                                      "favorite_count": 78,
                                      "favorited": false,
                                      "full_text": "🌳 Introducing Orchard — an open-source agentic modeling framework! 🎉\nOne thin &amp; cheap sandbox infra powers training recipes across SWE / GUI / personal-assistant agents:\n\n⚙️ Orchard Env: 0.28s exec latency; 100% success @ 1,000 parallel sandboxes 💪\n🛠️ Orchard-SWE: 67.5% on https://t.co/Jpnr0LE7MQ",
                                      "id_str": "2055163604614500451",
                                      "is_quote_status": false,
                                      "lang": "en",
                                      "possibly_sensitive": false,
                                      "possibly_sensitive_editable": true,
                                      "quote_count": 3,
                                      "reply_count": 0,
