                                                ],
                                                "url": "https://t.co/CVZCjANdwz"
                                              }
                                            ],
                                            "user_mentions": []
                                          },
                                          "id": "Tm90ZVR3ZWV0OjIwNTUxNjM2MDQ0NzYwMDIzMDQ=",
                                          "richtext": {
                                            "richtext_tags": []
                                          },
                                          "text": "🌳 Introducing Orchard — an open-source agentic modeling framework! 🎉\nOne thin & cheap sandbox infra powers training recipes across SWE / GUI / personal-assistant agents:\n\n⚙️ Orchard Env: 0.28s exec latency; 100% success @ 1,000 parallel sandboxes 💪\n🛠️ Orchard-SWE: 67.5% on SWE-bench Verified (30B-A3B, ~3B active)\n🖥️ Orchard-GUI: 68.4% avg on WebVoyager / Online-Mind2Web / DeepShop (4B!)\n📬 Orchard-Claw: 73.9% pass@3 on Claw-Eval\n \n🔗 https://t.co/CVZCjANdwz\n📦 Code and data are coming soon!\n\nLet's accelerate open agentic AI! 🚀"
                                        }
                                      }
                                    },
