                                "favorite_count": 397,
                                "favorited": false,
                                "full_text": "Soulva being so popular on Doordash is a sign of SF's lack of variety when it comes to quick dining options. \nTheir meats are drier than sand, their kale is rigid and bitter. It's such mid office-worker slop.",
