                            "favorite_count": 146,
                            "favorited": false,
                            "full_text": "🖥️ Risk assessment for terminal commands\n\nVS Code now shows a risk badge before you confirm a command, with an AI-generated explanation of what it actually does.\n\n🟢 Safe: reads files or prints output, no changes made.\n🟠 Caution: modifies your workspace, installs packages, or https://t.co/yu5Q3KKU70",
