                                "text": "🖥️ Risk assessment for terminal commands\n\nVS Code now shows a risk badge before you confirm a command, with an AI-generated explanation of what it actually does.\n\n🟢 Safe: reads files or prints output, no changes made.\n🟠 Caution: modifies your workspace, installs packages, or sends data over the network.\n🔴 Review carefully: may be difficult or impossible to undo.\n\nTo enable this experimental feature, open your settings and search for https://t.co/H353XEyKNk.riskAssessment.enabled"
                              }
                            }
