                                  "favorite_count": 140,
                                  "favorited": false,
                                  "full_text": "Fine, you all want to code like this I guess.\n\n(Runway's new Agent mode is quite impressive, doing fairly complex story building from just a short text description of what you want. Not error free obviously, but this was pretty great for a one-shot attempt) https://t.co/dO8lwbpgjK",
