                                      "favorite_count": 591,
                                      "favorited": false,
                                      "full_text": "Stop turning prompting into magic spells (and yes, this includes random slash commands with obscure outcomes).\n\nLet this one area of working with AI not be weird. Just ask for stuff, in well-specified formats, like a manager, not a sorcerer with a bunch of incantations.",
