                            "favorite_count": 16,
                            "favorited": false,
                            "full_text": "AI gives generic answers when your prompts are generic.\n\nThe fastest way to get more interesting outputs? Give it more specific, unexpected context.\n\nIn AI Prompting for Everyone, Andrew Ng shares practical techniques to help you get more useful, creative responses from AI https://t.co/yA0c3SAILf",
