                                  "full_text": "I'm building a new team at @databricks AI Research and we're hiring.\n\nWe're focused on one of the hardest open problems in AI right now: how do you measure and continuously improve agents that operate on enterprise data at scale. We're looking for founding engineers to build the",
                                  "id_str": "2055372210144210981",
