                                      "richtext": {
                                        "richtext_tags": []
                                      },
                                      "text": "I'm building a new team at @databricks AI Research and we're hiring.\n\nWe're focused on one of the hardest open problems in AI right now: how do you measure and continuously improve agents that operate on enterprise data at scale. We're looking for founding engineers to build the flywheel that turns evaluation results directly into better agents — from development and training all the way to production. \n\nIf you want to work on problems that actually matter at the frontier of AI research, I'd love to talk. \n\nLink in comments 👇"
                                    }
                                  }
                                },
