                                  "favorite_count": 933,
                                  "favorited": false,
                                  "full_text": "My team at HRT is hiring! We're building the best LLMs in the world for trading, from scratch. One of the few places in the world you can do real frontier LLM research, from pretraining to reasoning, powered by our incredible B200 cluster. Apply below!",
