                                      "favorite_count": 589,
                                      "favorited": false,
                                      "full_text": "New role! We're adding people to our LLM team, ASAP.\n\nWe already build some of the best models of markets. For LLMs, one must ask in 2026, why another one? We think we have a (unique) story, and are hiring for the full training stack - pre-to-post. Big resources, big ownership.",
