                                "full_text": "A milestone for Pearl Research Labs: our first major enterprise partnership is live with Together AI.\n@togethercompute’s inference platform is an ideal demonstration of @prlnet's value proposition — One of the world’s most advanced hyperscalers running AI workloads on Pearl’s",
