                                    "richtext": {
                                      "richtext_tags": []
                                    },
                                    "text": "A milestone for Pearl Research Labs: our first major enterprise partnership is live with Together AI.\n@togethercompute’s inference platform is an ideal demonstration of @prlnet's value proposition — One of the world’s most advanced hyperscalers running AI workloads on Pearl’s 2-for-1 Cuda kernels, turning inference into ¶PRL coins, and reducing consumer LLM price per token. Excited for what we’ll build together."
                                  }
                                }
