                                      "richtext": {
                                        "richtext_tags": []
                                      },
                                      "text": "Beau Rothrock had been at @AngelList for two months when he walked into a Redshift-to-Snowflake migration in deep trouble, already two months behind schedule.\n\nHe had a 5-week window to migrate all 14,000 dashboards and reports AngelList runs on.\n\nHe could've asked for three more engineers and four more months. Instead, he turned to Devin."
                                    }
                                  }
