                                  "favorite_count": 86,
                                  "favorited": false,
                                  "full_text": "Most AI tools give you a chat window.\n\nSai gives you a coworker with its own desktop.\n\nI told it: \"Do deep research on the topic.\"\n\nThen I closed my laptop.\n\nWhile I was off doing other work, Sai was inside its own secure Workspace - opening tabs, clicking through apps, reading https://t.co/cq7jHVcQnM",
                                  "id_str": "2055351198467911769",
                                  "is_quote_status": false,
                                  "lang": "en",
                                  "possibly_sensitive": false,
                                  "possibly_sensitive_editable": true,
                                  "quote_count": 1,
                                  "reply_count": 10,
                                  "retweet_count": 8,
                                  "retweeted": false,
                                  "user_id_str": "1573399256836309009"
                                },
                                "note_tweet": {
                                  "is_expandable": true,
                                  "note_tweet_results": {
                                    "result": {
                                      "entity_set": {
                                        "hashtags": [],
                                        "smarttags": [],
                                        "symbols": [],
                                        "timestamps": [],
                                        "urls": [],
                                        "user_mentions": []
                                      },
                                      "id": "Tm90ZVR3ZWV0OjIwNTUzNTExOTgzNjcyNTY1NzY=",
                                      "text": "Most AI tools give you a chat window.\n\nSai gives you a coworker with its own desktop.\n\nI told it: \"Do deep research on the topic.\"\n\nThen I closed my laptop.\n\nWhile I was off doing other work, Sai was inside its own secure Workspace - opening tabs, clicking through apps, reading sources, cross-referencing, taking notes. Not a chatbot summarizing a Google search. An actual coworker digging like a human does.\n\nWhen I came back, the research was done. Sources cited. Approvals requested before it sent anything. Nothing risky executed without my green light.\n\nThis is what an \"always-on\" computer-using agent actually looks like."
                                    }
                                  }
                                },
                                "rest_id": "2055351198467911769",
