                            "favorite_count": 22,
                            "favorited": false,
                            "full_text": "The first inference endpoint with @prlnet support, discounted by 25%, is live! \n\nThe endpoint generates @prlnet emissions to offset cost, and we’ll be discounting it further (and launching more endpoints) as Pearl spot prices change.",
